payload = ''
headers = {}

res = conn.getresponse()
data = res.read().decode('UTF-8')

In [14]:
def plotDot(point):
    folium.CircleMarker(location=[point.latitude, point.longitude],
                        radius=5,
                        weight=2,
                        popup = [point.Country,point.TotalConfirmed,point.TotalRecovered],
                        fill_color='#000000').add_to(m)
